# 🩺 Healtho – AI Healthcare Chatbot (Full Stack)

A full-stack AI healthcare chatbot with **41 diseases**, **132 symptoms**, content filtering, risk scoring, and Claude AI-powered chat.

---

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
healtho/
├── backend/          ← Express.js API (Node.js)
│   ├── server.js     ← Main server + ALL filters + Claude proxy
│   ├── package.json
│   └── .env.example
├── frontend/         ← React.js UI
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── App.js    ← Full UI (Chat + Symptom Checker + Disease Browser)
│   │   └── App.css
│   └── package.json
├── render.yaml       ← One-click deploy to Render
├── package.json      ← Root scripts (run both together)
└── .gitignore
```

---

## ⚡ Quick Start (Local)

### 1. Clone & Install
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/healtho-chatbot.git
cd healtho-chatbot
npm run install:all
```

### 2. Set API Key
```bash
cd backend
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env and add your Anthropic API key:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
```

### 3. Run Both Servers
```bash
# From root folder:
npm run dev
# Backend: http://localhost:5000
# Frontend: http://localhost:3000
```

---

## 🔒 All Filters Implemented

| Filter Type | What It Does |
|-------------|-------------|
| **Blocked content** | Blocks suicide, self-harm, weapons, illegal drugs |
| **Emergency detection** | Detects chest pain, stroke, seizure → 🚨 immediate alert |
| **Suspicious requests** | Warns on prescription/diagnosis requests |
| **Sensitive topics** | Flags pregnancy, infant, special conditions |
| **Input sanitization** | Strips HTML/script chars, limits to 500 chars |
| **Rate limiting** | 60 req/15min per IP, 10 chat/min |
| **Message length limit** | 500 character max |

---

## 🌐 Deploy to Render (Free)

1. Push code to GitHub
2. Go to [render.com](https://render.com) → New → Blueprint
3. Connect your GitHub repo
4. Render reads `render.yaml` and sets up both services automatically
5. Add `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` in the backend environment variables
6. Deploy! ✅

**Free tier**: Backend sleeps after 15 min idle (wakes in ~30s). Upgrade to Starter ($7/mo) for always-on.

